{
  "stem": "7600.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, I remember I always had people-- kids to play with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to go down the river Rhine and stop at one of these places and have a picnic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was just a wonderful day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just went for the day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we belonged to a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went-- always went on holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was, as I said, my parents decided not to be orthodox.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't go on Saturdays or Friday nights, except on the holidays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've preserved all the holidays-- Passover and, of course, Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My parents fasted on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the only time he closed the store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, and then Rosh Hashanah he closed the store on then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was open on Saturday mornings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody was open after noon anyway, in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Saturday was a 1/2 a day, and so he was open on Saturday mornings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he found that was important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we were definitely brought up Jewish and learned all of the-- about the holidays, and what it was all about, and all of the history, and all of this in the-- in the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother often said she's-- she couldn't stand the way she was brought up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father said the same thing, so they both agreed on that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was very good for us, I thought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were there a lot of Jewish people in the city?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were scattered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had some-- some kids that my parents knew that were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most of my friends were from school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, as I said, I went to an all girls school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were all girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no boys there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
